textAfterTable: Profile AXA World Funds - Euro 7-10 is an open-end investment fund incorporated in Luxembourg. The Fund's objective is to seek performance through dynamic exposure mainly to Euro zone bonds. The Fund invests in a diversified portfolio consisting of Euro zone government bonds and of any other quality bonds issued by corporations or public institutions denominated in Euro.
